<h2 id="Q4-%E2%80%94-Check-Data-Quality">Q4 — Check Data Quality<a class="anchor-link" href="#Q4-%E2%80%94-Check-Data-Quality">¶</a></h2><h2 id="Q4.1-%E2%80%94-Identify-columns-containing-null-values">Q4.1 — Identify columns containing null values<a class="anchor-link" href="#Q4.1-%E2%80%94-Identify-columns-containing-null-values">¶</a></h2><p>We'll show, for each column with nulls:</p>
<ul>
<li>the null count</li>
