<h2 id="Q5.1-%E2%80%94-Fill-Railcard-nulls-with-'None'">Q5.1 — Fill <code>Railcard</code> nulls with <code>'None'</code><a class="anchor-link" href="#Q5.1-%E2%80%94-Fill-Railcard-nulls-with-'None'">¶</a></h2><p>A null railcard means the passenger did not use one — that's a real category, not missing data.</p>
