<h2 id="Q5.2-%E2%80%94-Standardize-the-Reason-for-Delay-column">Q5.2 — Standardize the <code>Reason for Delay</code> column<a class="anchor-link" href="#Q5.2-%E2%80%94-Standardize-the-Reason-for-Delay-column">¶</a></h2><p>Steps:</p>
<ol>
<li>Strip extra whitespace</li>
<li>Convert to title case for consistent capitalisation</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea">
