<h2 id="Q5.3-%E2%80%94-Fill-the-remaining-Reason-for-Delay-nulls">Q5.3 — Fill the remaining <code>Reason for Delay</code> nulls<a class="anchor-link" href="#Q5.3-%E2%80%94-Fill-the-remaining-Reason-for-Delay-nulls">¶</a></h2><p>If the journey was <strong>On Time</strong>, the delay reason is logically <code>'No Delay'</code> — not missing data.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell">
