<h2 id="Q5.4-%E2%80%94-Handle-Actual-Arrival-Time-nulls">Q5.4 — Handle <code>Actual Arrival Time</code> nulls<a class="anchor-link" href="#Q5.4-%E2%80%94-Handle-Actual-Arrival-Time-nulls">¶</a></h2><p>These nulls correspond to <strong>Cancelled</strong> journeys — the train never arrived, so no time exists.
We <strong>keep</strong> these as null because filling them would be incorrect/misleading. This is a <em>justified</em> null.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
<div class="jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser">
</div>
