<h2 id="Q2-%E2%80%94-Revenue-by-Ticket-Type-&amp;-Ticket-Class">Q2 — Revenue by Ticket Type &amp; Ticket Class<a class="anchor-link" href="#Q2-%E2%80%94-Revenue-by-Ticket-Type-&amp;-Ticket-Class">¶</a></h2>
