<h1 id="Chart-6-%E2%80%94-Refund-Rate-by-Journey-Status-(Bar)">Chart 6 — Refund Rate by Journey Status (Bar)<a class="anchor-link" href="#Chart-6-%E2%80%94-Refund-Rate-by-Journey-Status-(Bar)">¶</a></h1>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell">
